OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDanish spy scandal:        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FEx-minister accused of     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fstate secrets leak         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Danish defence minister, Claus
OL,6, Hjort Frederiksen, said on Friday that 
OL,7, he had been charged under a law that   
OL,8, deals with divulging state secrets.    
OL,10,FHe did not say what he was accused of  
OL,11,Fleaking, but insisted he would never do
OL,12,Fanything to harm Denmark.              
OL,14,FOn Monday, it emerged a former foreign 
OL,15,Fintelligence chief was being held on   
OL,16,Fthe same charges.                      
OL,18,FLars Findsen, has been in prison for a 
OL,19,Fmonth, also for allegedly leaking      
OL,20,Ftop-secret information.                
